{
  "stem": "27509.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, I was-- as I mentioned, very early I had a very pessimistic point of view.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I, I saw no sense and no reason for self-delusion as I witnessed all around me among the adult population.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have decided that, in wartime, when conflagration is starting and just reaching you, the only thing to do is if you-- and you can't stand and fight anyhow, so you run away, especially if you've got the sort of an enemy that is-- with the Russians, you certainly couldn't.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't fight a, a, a actual war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You fought a political war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You fought a, an economic--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--ideological war, but not, not a,a war of-- actually.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I have decided to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I crossed the border to Wilno because Wilno [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] going to be taken over by the Lithuanians at the behest of the Russians.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Having occupied-- the Russians having occupied Wilno in their march westwards to meet the Germans, they were very generous to the Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They turned out [INAUDIBLE] the Lithuanians and said, Wilno is the nominal capital of Lithuania in your constitution-- since the First World War, occupied by the Poles.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to do the right thing by you, we will return Wilno to you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you can bring your capital of Lithuania from the little town of Kovno to its rightful place, Wilno.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and that's when the gratitude and the recognition of the Lithuanian population for the gesture of magnanimity.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Obviously, what they did is they've returned Wilno to the Lithuanians and then swallowed the whole of Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you need special papers to leave Bialystok?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I went-- I went illegally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went across the border illegally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
